2. Fetch users from an API and display only matching results.
3. Add a loading spinner while fetching.
4. Gracefully handle errors and empty results.
5. Bonus: Highlight the matched text in the results.

JSONPlaceholder API (https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/)

